author: Nate Scott
title: See the 3 covers for SI Swimsuit 2017 featuring Kate Upton | FOX Sports
text:
Feb 15, 2017 at 8:01a ET 0Shares 
Early on Wednesday Sports Illustrated released the three versions of the cover of this year's SI Swimsuit issue. They all feature Kate Upton, who makes her return to the cover after gracing it in both 2012 and 2013. Upton made her debut in SI Swimsuit in 2011. 
Yu Tsai Sports Illustrated 
You can find a lot more over at SI's Swimsuit page. Yu Tsai Sports Illustrated
